Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's all squirmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? An alien umbilical cord?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that put it in, you eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young ones, you mustn't waste food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu, you put chocolate in\Nthe damn napkins, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, you put in beer, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught me? But it deepens\Nthe flavor, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already so deep I can't\Ntell what tastes like what.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but may I open the curtain for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, as always, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,\Nwhat kind of training is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what the future holds in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must take that endless bit of\Ndarkness and turn it to our advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.16,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is practical training for doing just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking it in the dark,\Nit's not like beer at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hanuki-san is a mysterious dental hygienist\Nwho comes and goes under Master Higuchi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.16,0:01:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She lives on ethyl alcohol and Castellas,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and has a habit of getting\Ndrunk and licking people's faces.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you go drinking with Hanuki-san, you'd\Nbetter be prepared for an endless night of hell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was once freely dragged all around Kiyamachi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when I came to I was collapsed\Nnear the Ebisugawa power plant all alone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ozu was a person without\Neven a single point of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He could eat three\Nhelpings of people's misfortune.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although only 15 minutes earlier than me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Selfish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrogant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:54.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lazy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's Master Higuchi's first disciple,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he takes glory in\Nthis meaningless lifestyle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0} come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she has a report she can't get out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report I can't\Nget out of too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed, after neglecting my studies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and spending all day "training" for things,\Nsurrounded by these worthless faces,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have made a complete mess of\Nmy first two years of college life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a question that must be put\Nto the person responsible for this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is the one responsible? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the responsible party come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:23.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tatami Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I was a brand-spanking\Nnew freshman university student{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and before me lay open countless\Ndoors to that rose-colored campus life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, at that time I had a bad premonition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, at that time I had a bad premonition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:00.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciples Wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I could not envision{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}those suspicious-looking fliers\Nleading to some glorious future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must not reach out for these fliers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, I should get as far away as possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I was not able to escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciples Wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the clairvoyance to pick out\Nfair maidens from the crowds of Gion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and devil's ears that let not even the sound\Nof {\i1}sakura {\i0}falling into the canals slip past,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Higuchi Seitarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, ye youths of limitless possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bad premonition was right on the mark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had held a position of not\Nopening up my heart to anyone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as Master Higuchi lived in Yuusuisou,\Nthe same boarding house as I, we hit it off,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the fact that I was just old\Nenough to drink helped immediately...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Before long the walls came\Ndown and I was enjoying myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result of our heated\Narguments over boobs until dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is not whether\Nit is a real breast or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is whether you believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch, on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I ended up becoming his second disciple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course that was the only time\Nour Master ever treated us to alcohol.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being the disciple of Higuchi Seitarou...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm still not clear as to what I'm a\Ndisciple in even after these two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if you looked under the cover,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Higuchi was no hermit-master or\Nanything, but just some eighth-year student.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like how animals that live\Nlong lives feel somewhat uncanny,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our Master had this mysterious air\Nabout him unlike a normal person's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wore the same yukata and tall\Ngeta everywhere he went all year round,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and he knew 100 places\Nto cool off in the summer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He couldn't speak anything other than Japanese{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but could converse cordially\Nwith people in any country,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and there were times he perceived\Nthings that normal people did not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His body was light, and incredible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That being the case,\Nhe didn't participate in anything,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}only focusing intently\Non living life day-to-day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His was a frighteningly gentlemanly\Nmanner, perhaps the pinnacle of buffoonery.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, he had a weakness. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He had library fines. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Master was being targeted {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}by a secret collection organization\Nknown as the Library Police.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Helping him escape from them\Nwas our duty as his disciples.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides the Library Police, Master also had\Nan ongoing battle with a man named Jougasaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master called this battle the\N"Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as the name implies,\Nit was a "war" of the tiniest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}pettiest, stupidest things you could imagine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems that five years ago there\Nwas some deep strife between the two{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which caused the opening shots to be fired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}And we, as his disciples, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\i1}were wrapped up in this pointless struggle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Glued
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were wrapped up in this pointless struggle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For example, when we had\N20 plates of sushi delivered,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he'd invite over a bunch of\Nexchange students for a sushi party{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and me and Ozu would split the bill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In short, it was always us\Nwho got the short end of the stick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wondered if wasting my precious youth\Nhelping with this stuff was a good thing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but each day and the next\NI worked hard to pay him back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki is a perverted man the same year{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as Master Higuchi and\Nthe head of the movie circle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it's still uncertain what\Ngrudge they have between them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The journey is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the chaos just after the war in the Pacific,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}med students that stole the technique{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}behind tortoise-shaped scrubbing\Nbrushes from Nishio Market{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}created a mystical cleaning weapon\Nfrom the fibers of a palm that grew in Taiwan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tips of the fiber\Nwere both stiff and supple;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it seemingly used the Van der\NWaals force to bind dirt particles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so this company was put under pressure\Nby detergent makers for fear of losing sales.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As its power to clean was \Nconsidered too great a threat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1} it was banished to the depths of history;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, it seems like someone\Ncontinues to make them even now, in secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to obtain one of these\Nmystical tortoise scrubbing brushes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is another part of your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Master had required many things prior\Nto this, and we were always supplying him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do whatever you can\Nto get it by tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you're expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps he thought of\Ncleaning his 4.5 tatami room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but as you probably figured,\NI will be the one who ends up doing it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Master's room was so\Ndirty that at just one glance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a lady of sheltered\Nupbringing would surely swoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a disaster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wouldn't be surprised if it was some life form{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't plan to buy anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:52.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you makin' fun of me, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bring the salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that had never previously existed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}on the Earth's surface that secretly evolved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coming all the way to Sanjou Bridge, as it\Nwas lunch time, I saw fish and onions lined up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I'd rather shoot fireworks at them,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I had a feeling like I'd already done that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which made my uneasiness\Nall the more indescribable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I came to I had moved to Kiyamachi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and despite it still being mid-day, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}an old fortune teller \Nwas spreading out her eerie aura.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fortunes of this\Ncreature must surely be spot on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are unsatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you have fiercely earnest talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I tip my hat to the old woman's insight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I feel there's an\Nopportunity you can't let slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab the opportunity\Ndangling in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 4000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting more and more abridged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our Master made us do all kinds of\Nmeaningless things in the name of "training,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and most of them made no sense. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought a countless number\Nof times, "Why am I doing this?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I couldn't help but think,\N"If only I hadn't met the Master..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why shouldn't I just expel myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akashi-san is a first year in the engineering\Ndepartment like Ozu, and a younger disciple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mystical tortoise scrubbing brush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if it actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us search!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The old man I'd asked before,\Nwho was like a boiled octopus,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}acted nice like he'd just found\NPrincess Kaguya in a bamboo shoot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who runs a general store in\NWest Kinichiba might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the owner of the\Ngeneral store facing Bukkouji road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who runs the old book\Nstore over there might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The used utensil shop in\NShinkyougoku might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akashi-san was quite\Nskilled at information-gathering,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and narrowed down the location of the tortoise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're searching for the\Nmystical tortoise scrubbing brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about the mystical...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hear of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how much for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I will ask for 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I'm buying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No scrubbing brush is worth 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you'd wash in a sink of a\N4.5 tatami boarding house covered in sludge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. I give up on the scrubbing brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Master is not going\Nto cut the thread so trivially.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will ask him as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ If I can become a circle with you... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,At the public bath
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Farewell triangle; I'll\Ncome back sometime, square. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Circle X triangle... Always a dead space. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The world tends to 4 sides,\N4 faces, 5 sides, 6 sides, turkey. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Search for the circle... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Search for the circle... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ To learn how not to become a circle... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It might be nowhere. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It might be somewhere. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ You don't know either... On this Kamo River. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Search for the circle... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Search for the circle. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I was listening to my Master's song,\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suddenly had a feeling like he\Nwould be going somewhere far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi-{\i1}kun {\i0}and Jougasaki-{\i1}kun {\i0}\Nwere here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It had been a long time since they'd met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}'s pretty cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Higuchi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}is all that different, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-{\i1}kun {\i0}hasn't had any other\Nfriends than Higuchi-{\i1}kun {\i0}since long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think that Higuchi-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}is going to make you his successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't think I'm suited to\Nliving in such a shrewd manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when two high\Nschool seniors were rivals in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it was a drinking\Ncontest with unrefined {\i1}sake{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the details are already\Nlost to the depths of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so this battle dragged on for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they refused to let it drop\Nwithout coming to a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in their utter desperation,\Nthey thought up the Proxy War.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They forgot the reason\Nfor the battle's beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and, without regard to changes in society,\Npassed it down through successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically it's called the Masochistic\NProxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-\NProxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy-Proxy War.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking it over, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I came back, there was a\Nbag left in my room I did not know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funds for continuing the Proxy War?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what's what anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was precisely the amount of\Nmoney needed to buy the tortoise brush!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I take the Eizan Electric up to\NKurama and hide out as Ushiwakamaru?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or should I take the Kyoto-Osaka and head\Naround Naniwa with some raven-haired maidens?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was called a Mochiguman, and\NAkashi-san had once told me she had lost it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems they come in\Nsets of five and she lost one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please grab the opportunity\Nthat is dangling in front of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dream Date with Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will let myself be expelled! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this 100,000 yen I should\Nreturn to the life I deserve!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this you have cleared the final test!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I did everything the Master said\Nthese past two years just to see this smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a ceremony now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I have something important to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dual on the Kamo-oohashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Proxy-Proxy War will continue with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so the cannons were\Nreadied for the decisive battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jougasaki came walking from the West side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two soon met in the\Ncenter of the Kamooohashi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akashi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again. How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I'm fit and healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are one of Higuchi's?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I became his disciple last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And isn't that my disciple, Ozu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my proxy, the one who will succeed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have thought he was your disciple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was actually my spy, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fool you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is unprecedented in the history\Nof the Masochistic Proxy-Proxy War.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name will be etched into history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things sure dragged out for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it five years? Or more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten. It's been\Na battle of so many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ozu was active in all fields, and\Ndespite filming a hit-piece on Jougasaki,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it seems he also dyed\NMaster Higuchi's yukata pink,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and played the part of a\Nmeaningless double agent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy is your proxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it over with already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The battle started with such a flat phrase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a moment's breath the two clashed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock-Paper-Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jougasaki-{\i1}kun {\i0}won, so Ozu-{\i1}kun {\i0}goes first next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weight has finally\Nbeen lifted from my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanuki. Higuchi is spouting some nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I plan on circling the globe once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me, Hanuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can speak English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be crazy. This is foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the prize money from the Shimanami Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, sorry about this, but\Nplease clean up the room with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so my Master disappeared with the wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go out for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally in the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who spends\Nall that money on your love-doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu-{\i1}kun{\i0}. He tells me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his real story anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I might rather\Njump into the Kamo River.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or maybe run away from Kyoto to\NMurotomisaki and obtain enlightenment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I look forward to our time together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I apologize if you were supposed to bat first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's continue to play nice and dirty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first shot of the\NProxy-Proxy War had been fired.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being caught by Master\NHiguchi in front of that clock tower{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was surely a turning point of my fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I had joined some other circle, I would\Nhave surely spent quite a different two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Clearly meeting Ozu was my greatest mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
